      • setSkipNullDates

        public void setSkipNullDates(boolean value)

      • setSkipEmptyRepeaters

        public void setSkipEmptyRepeaters(boolean value)
        If true, blank cells will not be added to the extraProperties map and therefore will be left off of the node. This will keep repeating attributes from migrating with a single blank String at index 0.
